4️⃣ Raspberry Pi Camera Overview

The Pi camera module is a small camera designed for Raspberry Pi.

Features:

5MP / 8MP resolution

HD video recording

Supports image capture

Supports computer vision libraries

The camera connects using CSI interface (Camera Serial Interface).

5️⃣ Camera Connection

Steps:

1️⃣ Locate CSI port on Raspberry Pi
2️⃣ Insert ribbon cable carefully
3️⃣ Lock the connector
4️⃣ Reboot the Raspberry Pi

6️⃣ Enable Camera Interface

