Components Required

(List components)

Theory

RFID (Radio Frequency Identification) is a wireless technology used for automatic identification of objects using radio waves.

The RFID reader communicates with Raspberry Pi through SPI interface to read tag information.

Each RFID tag contains a unique identification number.

Circuit Diagram

Draw:

RFID Module → Raspberry Pi SPI pins

Algorithm

Enable SPI interface

Initialize RFID reader

Detect RFID card

Read UID

Display card information

Program

