Download Raspberry Pi Imager

Insert SD card

Install Raspberry Pi OS

Boot Raspberry Pi

Configure system settings

Update OS

Enable interfaces

1️⃣5️⃣ Journal Writing Format
Title

Starting Raspberry Pi OS (Raspbian OS)

Aim

To install and start Raspberry Pi OS on Raspberry Pi board.

Components Required

(List components)

Theory

Raspberry Pi OS is a Linux-based operating system used for Raspberry Pi devices.

It provides support for programming languages, GPIO control, and IoT development.

Procedure

Download Raspberry Pi Imager

Install OS on SD card

Insert SD card into Raspberry Pi

Power ON Raspberry Pi

Configure system settings

Output

Raspberry Pi successfully booted into Raspberry Pi OS desktop environment.

Result

Raspberry Pi OS installed and system ready for IoT development.

1️⃣6️⃣ Viva Questions

Q: What is Raspberry Pi?
→ Small single-board computer used for embedded systems.

Q: What OS does Raspberry Pi use?
→ Raspberry Pi OS (Linux based).

Q: What is SD card used for?
→ Storage and operating system boot.

Q: What is GPIO?
→ General Purpose Input Output pins used for hardware interaction.

Q: What is Linux?
→ Open-source operating system.

